- **Game Instance:** `/Source/LFP2D/Core/LFPGameInstance.h`
- **World Map:** `/Source/LFP2D/WorldMap/LFPWorldMapGameMode.h`, `LFPWorldMapPlayerState.h`, `LFPWorldMapNode.h`
- **Unit:** `/Source/LFP2D/Unit/LFPTacticsUnit.h`
- **Battle Types:** `/Source/LFP2D/Turn/LFPBattleTypes.h`

