## Implementation Plan: Party & Reserve Roster System

### Overview

This plan adds a lightweight party/reserve roster system that persists across level transitions via `ULFPGameInstance`. It covers 7 areas: the unit entry struct, a unit registry data asset, party/reserve storage on GameInstance, battle result modification for captured units, battle-side capture tracking, post-battle processing on the world map, and a replacement UI widget.

